overview: The user initiated a review of a sleep questionnaire application,
  providing a Statement of Work and a detailed questionnaire. The assistant
  performed a comprehensive analysis, identifying both well-implemented features
  and significant gaps. A detailed plan was then created, prioritizing missing
  elements such as a tiredness severity scale, COMISA detection, and outbound
  links in the report. The assistant has begun executing this plan, successfully
  integrating a 1-10 severity scale for tiredness, complete with dynamic safety
  warnings in both the questionnaire interface and the generated report. This
  involved updating data types, validation schemas, and UI components to reflect
  the new severity assessment.
